title: 820-2936-B error code 4sns/1/C0000008: TC0D--124 FAN SPINNING FAST
message:
The first 3 temp sensor fails are U5510 having no communication to the SMC.TH1H is U5520, but that usually also causes TP0P error.

Run the EFI version of ASD and see what the exact error is. ASD version is not very good for that.

I'm suspecting there is crap under the SMC seeing that there is more than one SMBUS involved in these errors.
